'''差异甲基化区'''（{{lang-en|Differentially methylated regions}}，'''DMRs'''）指在多种样本（组织、细胞、个体等）中[[基因组|基因组]]里[[甲基化|甲基化]]状态不相同的区域，被看作为可能参与[[基因|基因]]转录水平调控的功能性区域。在多种组织中鉴定DMRs（T-DMRs）综合考察了人类组织中[[表观遗传学|表观遗传学]]的差异<ref>{{cite journal|last=Rakyan|first=VK|coauthors=Down, TA; Thorne, NP; Flicek, P; Kulesha, E; Gräf, S; Tomazou, EM; Bäckdahl, L; Johnson, N; Herberth, M; Howe, KL; Jackson, DK; Miretti, MM; Fiegler, H; Marioni, JC; Birney, E; Hubbard, TJ; Carter, NP; Tavaré, S; Beck, S|title=An integrated resource for genome-wide identification and analysis of human tissue-specific differentially methylated regions (tDMRs)|journal=Genome research|date=2008 Sep|year=2008|volume=18|issue=9|pages=1518–29|pmid=18577705|doi=10.1101/gr.077479.108|pmc=2527707}}</ref>。[[癌症|癌症]]与正常样品间的DMRs（C-DMRs）展示出癌症中甲基化缺失情况<ref>{{cite journal|last=Irizarry|first=RA|coauthors=Ladd-Acosta, C; Wen, B; Wu, Z; Montano, C; Onyango, P; Cui, H; Gabo, K; Rongione, M; Webster, M; Ji, H; Potash, JB; Sabunciyan, S; Feinberg, AP|title=The human colon cancer methylome shows similar hypo- and hypermethylation at conserved tissue-specific CpG island shores|journal=Nature genetics|date=2009 Feb|volume=41|issue=2|pages=178–86|pmid=19151715|doi=10.1038/ng.298|pmc=2729128}}</ref>。众所周知，[[DNA甲基化|DNA甲基化]]与细胞分化及增殖有关<ref>{{cite journal|last=Reik|first=W|coauthors=Dean, W; Walter, J|title=Epigenetic reprogramming in mammalian development|journal=Science|date=2001-08-10|volume=293|issue=5532|pages=1089–93|pmid=11498579|doi=10.1126/science.1063443}}</ref>，现找到发育阶段（D-DMRs<ref>{{cite journal|last=Meissner|first=A|coauthors=Mikkelsen, TS; Gu, H; Wernig, M; Hanna, J; Sivachenko, A; Zhang, X; Bernstein, BE; Nusbaum, C; Jaffe, DB; Gnirke, A; Jaenisch, R; Lander, ES|title=Genome-scale DNA methylation maps of pluripotent and differentiated cells|journal=Nature|date=2008-08-07|volume=454|issue=7205|pages=766–70|pmid=18600261|bibcode=2008Natur.454..766M|doi=10.1038/nature07107|pmc=2896277}}</ref>）及重编程阶段（R-DMRs<ref>{{cite journal|last=Doi|first=A|coauthors=Park, IH; Wen, B; Murakami, P; Aryee, MJ; Irizarry, R; Herb, B; Ladd-Acosta, C; Rho, J; Loewer, S; Miller, J; Schlaeger, T; Daley, GQ; Feinberg, AP|title=Differential methylation of tissue- and cancer-specific CpG island shores distinguishes human induced pluripotent stem cells, embryonic stem cells and fibroblasts|journal=Nature genetics|date=2009 Dec|volume=41|issue=12|pages=1350–3|pmid=19881528|doi=10.1038/ng.471|pmc=2958040}}</ref>）中存在的许多DMRs。此外还存在着个体内DMRs（Intra-DMRs），这种DMRs在给定的个体中随着年龄的增长而在全局DNA甲基化过程中发生纵向改变<ref>{{cite journal|last=Bjornsson|first=HT|coauthors=Sigurdsson, MI; Fallin, MD; Irizarry, RA; Aspelund, T; Cui, H; Yu, W; Rongione, MA; Ekström, TJ; Harris, TB; Launer, LJ; Eiriksdottir, G; Leppert, MF; Sapienza, C; Gudnason, V; Feinberg, AP|title=Intra-individual change over time in DNA methylation with familial clustering|journal=JAMA : the journal of the American Medical Association|date=2008-06-25|volume=299|issue=24|pages=2877–83|pmid=18577732|doi=10.1001/jama.299.24.2877|pmc=2581898}}</ref>。也有个体间DMRs（Inter-DMRs），这种DMRs在不同个体间存在差异甲基化类型<ref>{{cite journal|last=Bock|first=C|coauthors=Walter, J; Paulsen, M; Lengauer, T|title=Inter-individual variation of DNA methylation and its implications for large-scale epigenome mapping|journal=Nucleic acids research|date=2008 Jun|volume=36|issue=10|pages=e55|pmid=18413340|doi=10.1093/nar/gkn122|pmc=2425484}}</ref>。

==鉴定差异甲基化区的工具==
QDMR（定量差异甲基化区）is a quantitative approach to quantify methylation difference and identify DMRs from genome-wide methylation profiles by adapting [[Shannon_entropy|Shannon entropy]] (https://web.archive.org/web/20151023040525/http://bioinfo.hrbmu.edu.cn/qdmr/). The platform-free and species-free nature of QDMR makes it potentially applicable to various methylation data. This approach provides an effective tool for the high-throughput identification of the functional regions involved in epigenetic regulation. QDMR can be used as an effective tool for the quantification of methylation difference and identification of DMRs across multiple samples.<ref>{{cite journal|last=Zhang|first=Y|coauthors=Liu, H; Lv, J; Xiao, X; Zhu, J; Liu, X; Su, J; Li, X; Wu, Q; Wang, F; Cui, Y|title=QDMR: a quantitative method for identification of differentially methylated regions by entropy|journal=Nucleic acids research|date=2011 May|volume=39|issue=9|pages=e58|pmid=21306990|doi=10.1093/nar/gkr053|pmc=3089487}}</ref>

